{"tid":1947474,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"西班牙指華測試劑準確度不足30%","createTime":"2020-03-28T10:08:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-29T11:11:51.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7ecfdc93387caf9451477be7984481db077a0384","tid":1947474,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T10:08:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200328/Z6HIBDO2HXJGDS6VWR6JRMFSOQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200328%2FZ6HIBDO2HXJGDS6VWR6JRMFSOQ%2F&d=g1YLBr7c5t2fgTVFseaOq1EyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=56b4a0af\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200328%2FZ6HIBDO2HXJGDS6VWR6JRMFSOQ%2F&h=eb432377\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200328/Z6HIBDO2HXJGDS6VWR6JRMFSOQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n西班牙指華測試劑準確度不足30%<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200328/large/1585326128_ddd5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200328%2Flarge%2F1585326128_ddd5.gif&h=63f04728&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n西班牙醫護人員在醫院外與聲援民眾擁抱。<br />\n<br />\n西班牙前日（26日）指中國一批9,000套病毒快速檢測試劑不合格，準確度不足30%。中國駐西班牙大使館昨急出面割席，稱該批貨品是西班牙向某家深圳公司購買，非向中國官方購買；深圳市監局已展開調查。涉事公司則推諉指這或因西班牙醫療人員採樣有問題，導致檢測準確度下降。<br />\n<br />\n西班牙日前從深圳易瑞生物等公司買進64萬套病毒快速檢測試劑，結果9,000套試劑準確度僅20%至30%，許多陽性患者竟呈陰性。西班牙為此向中國退回有缺陷試劑，中國駐西班牙大使館昨在Twitter割席，指為廠商問題。<br />\n<br />\n華使館急割席<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：機舖 戲院 健身中心今起停業  座位削半 食肆攬炒<br />\n<br />\n中國駐西班牙大使館指，易瑞生物並未得中國國家藥品監督管理局的批准販售產品，中國商務部向西班牙的供應商清單，也不包括易瑞生物；同時表示，該批快速檢測試劑與中西兩國達成的4.32億歐元（約37億港元）醫療物資採購合作無關。<br />\n<br />\n深圳市場監管昨日周五（27日）稱已開始核查事件；易瑞生物同日發聲明：「經了解，（西班牙的醫院）在採樣和樣本提取過程中，可能沒嚴格按照我司的操作使用說明來進行鼻咽拭子樣本的採樣、提取和操作，因此導致樣本檢測準確度下降。」<br />\n<br />\n據悉，西班牙衞生部決定要求易瑞生物更換新批次的產品，並繼續執行雙方合同，同時要求易瑞生物按時交付相關產品，保障西班牙抗疫物資供應。<br />\n<br />\nTwitter/《自由時報》"},{"pid":"b5acbca474f58e4c17248238b4fe613d16e1522e","tid":1947474,"uid":173404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T10:09:35.000Z","msg":"Ciao ciao ciao<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55e70cb13377bd98c4f04313bf023272c035abe8","tid":1947474,"uid":321977,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T10:10:47.000Z","msg":"支那:有30%仲想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4267028a2a6f0f9ac5470644693a61523662338","tid":1947474,"uid":293012,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T10:12:05.000Z","msg":"支那：你用錯左姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff28ac7724bf45a8c958c2dcf8db0bc2483636c2","tid":1947474,"uid":9193,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T10:15:07.000Z","msg":"鳩估都50 50啦 真係斷鳩估好過"},{"pid":"598cde604fbc905f66281968694e642979fa12b1","tid":1947474,"uid":297997,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T10:16:24.000Z","msg":"信中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只可以話抵撚死"},{"pid":"52aa1d51a578a4bfcd1cc5b232f10e8ca19d1e53","tid":1947474,"uid":267488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T11:11:51.000Z","msg":"西班牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}